Package: knowledgeSharing
Title: Knowledge Sharing Analysis via Sliding Window Centroids
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Christopher",
           family = "Holland",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "you@example.com")
Description: Analyze how conversational semantics shift over time by computing 
    centroids over sliding windows in a shared LSA space. Provides windowed centroid
    trajectories, cosine similarity to previous windows, and plotting helpers.
